  {
    id: "item1",
    title: "What is this starter template?",
    content:
      "This is a minimal Astro starter template with essential components designed for easy customization. It includes a flexible grid system, typography, and common UI components.",
  },
  {
    id: "item2",
    title: "How do I customize the components?",
    content:
      "Each component uses predictable class names and minimal styling. You can override styles in your main stylesheet, use CSS custom properties, or create new variant classes.",
  },
  {
    id: "item3",
    title: "Are the components accessible?",
    content:
      "Yes! All components follow WCAG guidelines and include proper ARIA attributes, semantic HTML, keyboard navigation support, and focus management.",
  },
