  {
    id: "faq1",
    title: "Installation & Setup",
    htmlContent:
      "<p>Clone the repository, run <code>npm install</code>, and start the development server with <code>npm run dev</code>.</p><p>The template includes all necessary dependencies and configurations.</p>",
