    id: "faq3",
    title: "Performance Considerations",
    htmlContent:
      "<p>The template is optimized for performance with:</p><ul><li>Minimal CSS footprint</li><li>Tree-shaking support</li><li>Efficient component architecture</li><li>Scoped styles to prevent conflicts</li></ul>",
